<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7967290>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Map of the Indo-Burma region with the known distribution of Gekko mizoramensis sp. n. (1) Lawngtlai (type locality ‘black star’), (2) Thingkah, (3) Hnahthial, (4) Thenhlum, (5) Dampa Tiger Reserve, (6) Mizoram University Campus, (7) Kolasib, (8) Pualreng Wildlife Sanctuary and (9) Sangu Wildlife Sanctuary (BHUIYAN et al 2020). Map generated with QGIS." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7967290/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

